ill" title="Harry M. Caudill">Harry M. Caudill</a>, <a href="/wiki/Wallace_Stegner" title="Wallace Stegner">Wallace Stegner</a>, <a href="/wiki/Thomas_Merton" title="Thomas Merton">Thomas Merton</a>, <a href="/wiki/Southern_Agrarians" title="Southern Agrarians">Southern Agrarians</a></dd>
