<p><a name="Awards" id="Awards"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Wendell_Berry&amp;action=edit&amp;section=12" title="Edit section: Awards">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Awards</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Guggenheim_Fellowship" title="Guggenheim Fellowship">Guggenheim Fellowship</a> &amp; <a href="/wiki/Rockefeller_Fellowship" title="Rockefeller Fellowship" class="mw-redirect">Rockefeller Fellowships</a></li>
